{"title":"县报记者谈宝山","authors":["邹荻帆"],"dates":[{"year":1958,"month":6,"day":10}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"县报记者谈宝山"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"邹荻帆"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"记者从山区回来，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"手上捧着云母、水晶矿……"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"“我到的山地呀，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"山上满是花果香。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"山地好似描花的大宝柜，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"宝柜里有无尽的宝藏！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"“随便踢一脚吧，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"脚尖就有矿石发亮。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"人们可说这是穷山，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"今天才让宝山发光。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"“人们打开了宝柜，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"深山寻宝，大手采矿。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"新奇迹从指头出现，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"水泉在地层流响。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"“你知道这里需要水吗？"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"二十里外运水，汗水直淌，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"等雪水、望雨水、靠天吃天，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"舌焦唇枯跟干旱的梯田一样……"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"“宝藏到处都是，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"党给了我们钥匙去打开百宝箱。”"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":8,"page_end":8}